<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pleached" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pleached,</orth> intertwined, interwoven: <cit><quote>steal into the p. bower,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with p. arms,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.14.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 14, 73</bibl></cit> (folded). cf. <emph>Even-pleached, Impleached, Thick-pleached.</emph>
